sentences.english: That is because Malian government forces are fighting against rebels .

sentences.english: And yet outsiders could still help Somalis to help themselves.

sentences.english: Marylebone Station was packed with homeward- bound commuters.

sentences.english: That day was hastened when the sea-brigands of Somalia caught Chinese vessels, cargoes and sailors in the net of their brazen raids.

sentences.english: The senior showcase is a highlight of our year at the Maryland School of the Arts.

sentences.english: Malloy says that you like fat women.
